OL,3,C'Robbery mastermind' takes stand in PC
OL,4,Cmurder trial
OL,6,FThe alleged mastermind of an armed
OL,7,Frobbery in which a police officer was
OL,8,Fshot dead has told his murder trial he
OL,9,F"never" went in the building where it
OL,10,Fhappened.
OL,12,FPiran Ditta Khan gave evidence at
OL,13,FLeeds Crown Court on Friday ` more
OL,14,Fthan 18 years after PC Sharon
OL,15,FBeshenivsky was killed in Bradford.
