OL,3,C'Robbery mastermind' takes stand in PC
OL,4,Cmurder trial
OL,6,FThe mother-of-three, who was 38, was
OL,7,Fresponding to a raid at Universal
OL,8,FExpress travel agent in Morley Street
OL,9,Fon 18 November 2005 when she died. Her
OL,10,Fcolleague, PC Teresa Milburn, was
OL,11,Fseriously injured.
OL,13,FThe court has heard seven men were
OL,14,Finvolved in carrying out the robbery.
OL,15,FMr Khan is the last to face trial.
OL,17,FHe was arrested in Pakistan in January
OL,18,F2020, before being charged with murder
OL,19,Fand extradited to the UK.
