OL,6,FMr Khan said Hassan Razzaq, one of the
OL,7,Fseven men who went on to carry out the
OL,8,Frobbery, offered to "get his money
OL,9,Fback".
OL,11,FHe said: "I asked him 'How will you
OL,12,Fget the money?' He said: 'Uncle you
OL,13,Fleave that to me'."
OL,15,FMr Khan said Razzaq never told him how
OL,16,Fhe would to get the money back.
