OL,6,FHe told the court: "He doesn't look
OL,7,Flike a gangster to me, he was well
OL,8,Fdressed, well spoken, I wasn't
OL,9,Fthinking 'he's a gangster'. To me he's
OL,10,Fa very polite man."
OL,12,FMr Khan told the court he came to the
OL,13,FUK from Pakistan as a teenager in
OL,14,F1965, initially living in Bradford.
OL,16,FAt the time of the robbery he was
OL,17,Fliving in London.
