OL,6,FThe court was given details about his
OL,7,Fbackground, including that he was
OL,8,Filliterate and worked in a biscuit
OL,9,Ffactory.
OL,11,FMr Khan asked to sit during evidence
OL,12,Fbecause of ill health, including skin
OL,13,Fcancer and arthritis.
OL,15,FThree men have already been convicted
OL,16,Fof murder. Two others were found
OL,17,Fguilty of manslaughter, along with
OL,18,Frobbery and firearms offences. A sixth
OL,19,Fwas convicted of robbery.
