OL,6,FThe court has previously heard
OL,7,Fprosecution claims that, while Mr Khan
OL,8,Fwas not one of the three men who
OL,9,Fcarried out the robbery, and did not
OL,10,Fshoot PC Beshenivsky, he "was
OL,11,Fresponsible for organising this
OL,12,Frobbery in the knowledge that loaded
OL,13,Ffirearms were to be carried".JMr Khan
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty in October last year to
OL,15,Frobbery but denies murder and firearms
OL,16,Foffences.
OL,18,FThe trial continues.
